# Quote Generator Training Manual

This manual enumerates all field options and every possible permutation of the quote generator inputs.

## Field Options

- **Loan Type**: Bridge, Term, Development
- **Interest Calculation Type**: Retained, Service, Service + Capital, Capital, Flexible
- **Amount Input**: Gross, Net
- **Gross Amount**: Fixed, Percentage
- **Currency**: GBP, EUR
- **Interest Rate**: Monthly Rate, Annual Rate
- **Interest Calculation**: Simple, Daily, Monthly, Quarterly
- **Payment Timing**: Advance, Arrears
- **Payment Frequency**: Monthly, Quarterly
- **Loan End**: Term (months), End Date
- **LTV Targeting Simulation**: TRUE, FALSE
